headline: Aterian Announces Availability of hOmeLabs Dehumidifiers on HomeDepot.com

headline: What Recent Price Drops Mean for Home Depot’s True Value in 2025
summary: If you are wondering what to make of Home Depot’s stock right now, you are far from alone. After a steady climb over the past few years, with gains of more than 40% in three years and nearly 57% over five, Home Depot now finds itself in a patch of volatility. The stock closed recently at $385.75, but has drifted down 1.3% in the past week and is off 5.9% for the past month. While those short-term moves might have some investors nervous, others see it as evidence of a market finally coming to...
